Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a BETA version
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy watching! I love you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the timer goes off, please open your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you open your eyes, you will forget all you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have said and experienced while your eyes were closed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still daydreaming, Kiyora!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your hand doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly decide when to do our repeat-performance,\Nas we have to begin practicing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.81,0:01:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat-performance? Are you really sure we can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.04,0:01:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Didn't you read the newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.17,0:01:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!\NNope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.57,0:01:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai-yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.52,0:01:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.52,0:01:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rising Star is well received.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaaa, I didn't expect that we can gain profits..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Let me contact all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat-performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.89,0:01:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Repeat-performance? Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's fine with me but next time let me perform\Ncello concerto!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind, I'm already working on it now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Repeat-performance Decided!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha? Why? But didn't you suddenly call me,\Nsaying that you wanted to eat ramen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Senpai's not afraid of going by airplane anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a starter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what about going to Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And by the way, why must it be Hokkaido?\NIs there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No..nothing..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, just to eat ramen we're going to Hokkaido??
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, the way of thinking of the RICH is different!!\NBut I feel bad, that you're taking me too. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's dangerous to go alone, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But two guys going to Hokkaido, hmm....\NHa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But two guys going to Hokkaido, hmm....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.38,0:02:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow it is odd, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why if we took Masumi too, it would be odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masumi-chan! Just when we were talking about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-eh, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yourself, what are you doing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you turn off your cell phone?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves can affect the plane,\Nwhat if the plane falls down?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn it off when entering the plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:02:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Turn it off NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are announcing the latest information for Japan\NSky Airlines to Sapporo Flight no 733.\NPassengers are asked to come aboard....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Your face is so pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel well?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nnn...no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay let's go!\NLet's go eat ramen! Ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. Let me check your seatbelts. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please don't worry about us
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really not is such relationship....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing!\NYou're making me feel very uncomfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plane will take off soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.09,0:03:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:03:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please try it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Senpai's not afraid of going by plane anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame Cantabile\NLesson 9
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:05:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not distribute this softsubs.\Nhttp://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I did fly across that sky, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go abroad now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody wants Rising Star's autograph\N(somebody mailed/called him)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.05,0:05:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An everlasting orchestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a big step in my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Let's do sightseeing straightaway!\NYes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yosh! Let's do sightseeing straightaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually it's my first time in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! As we're here, let's stay overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay overnight here, we can eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's buy crabs and go home....Crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do they sell crabs here? Crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! But we were going to that direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Chiaki! It's ramen that you came here for, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.57,0:06:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please buy a lot of crabs for Nodame...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.61,0:06:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"horsehair crabs"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,snow crabs "6000 yen/box"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huah!!\Nsnow crabs "6000 yen/box"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"8000 yen/box"\NHuah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I also want to eat a few sea urchins
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huehhh??
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sea urchins!!!!\N"15.000 yen/box"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeeeeek!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, also ramen and yubari melon and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,....Shiroi Aijin...(White Lover chocolates)\N(the joke: changing "Koibito" to "Aijin", and the\Nmeaning became negative in nuance!)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyora, sorry that I am poor...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Shinichi flew by plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he alright with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time Shinichi said by himself that\Nhe was going go to by plane...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is thanks to this girl, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King Crabs"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Purple Sea Urchins" (expensive)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Scallops"\N(in the brown bag)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Chiaki Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'll be away for a while,\Nplease water this kid for me.\N(=plant in the pot)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,LOVE Nodame
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noda
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame's staying at Harisen's house??
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.56,0:07:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said as she couldn't come here for a while,\Nshe came to return the accumulated plates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bzzzz...bzzz...bzzzz\N(=it stinks in here!! Urghh!)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Chiaki-san..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thank you for taking care of Ryuutaro in Hokkaido
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he said sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that he didn't buy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King Crabs"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..any crabs..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually I love crabs very much..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece embodying the love between Senpai and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi! No such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Schubert? Beethoven?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to sleep again?\NAfter eating so much breakfast??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.88,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Come on!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The piece for the first stage of competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to choose between Schubert and Beethoven??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right...\NUmm..the piece to play in the competition, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I choose this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schumann
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Schubert!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oops, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, you! Do you seriously want to do it??
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Very much!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already practiced it too in preparation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play it rightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.46,0:09:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she really studied hard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame....will participate in competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroshiku onegaishimasu!!\N(=used when asking a favor, kindness, teachings etc)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I was glad she said it on her own will,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why so suddenly.....?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew???\NIt was sloppy halfway!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it? Can I win with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win, you said? Do you mean you want to win\N1st place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't take lessons properly until just a\Nshort while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how could you possibly win 1st place??!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competitions are not such an easy thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the time you spent for preparation is short!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This participation now is just for an experience to\Nprepare you for next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next year will be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who entered a competition in order to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.17,0:10:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially this Maradonna Piano Competition
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will give 2.000.000 yen as the Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, it will give scholarship to study abroad\Nfor the the one winning the 1st place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that it was the reason why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CERTAINLY I am going to win 2.000.000 yen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ARE YOU STUPID??!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to enter a competition with money as the target??!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That amount is enough to go to Europe, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Europe??
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.51,0:10:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough to follow Senpai, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Competition...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.68,0:10:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame's really in Harisen's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually what does she have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no....are you peeping or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaa Chiaki-kun??
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaaaaa ....yes you're really Chiakun!!\NIt's been a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yaaa..you're handsome as usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.51,0:11:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaori-san too, you have not changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up? Did you come here to become\Nmy husband's pupil again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!! What are those? Crabs?\NOmiyage? For me?\N(=gifts from a trip)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I went to Hokkaido for a  short trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are omiyage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me? All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This evening, please eat them TO-GE-THER with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Sensei giving in-training again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And it has been a while since he was\Nso enthusiastic....my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pupil is going to take part in\NMaradonna Piano Competition, it seems..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Maradonna?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, until the competition is over, she will stay with us\Nto have special training, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, for in-training like this,\Nshe's the only one beside Chiaki-kun, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore I wonder if she's really an excellent student?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame's in competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booboo! Nodame's in competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame won't participate in any competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame will be a kindergarten teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.81,0:12:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...when she hated it so much before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Schubert's Sonata....Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow it's an odd Schubert, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's messy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a piano player made for competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that her sound and technique are very good,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I also understand Harisen's feelings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play it so sloppily!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is becoming like Chopin now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to change the scale!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Harisen can fix this weak point of hers
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I'll go home now
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Already going home?\NEh, let's eat the crabs together!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...I don't want to disturb all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good bye..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody knows until she does it
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important is..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.60,0:13:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if Nodame seriously wants to play the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,perhaps it is good to trust Harisen to coach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 44 messages
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, Masumi here.\NWhere are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, Masumi here.\NWhere are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, Masumi here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.11,0:14:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama, Masumi here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama....Masumi here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama.......
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.14,0:14:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!\NChiaki-Sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama.........
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chi...Chi...Chiaki....Chi....Chiaki...Chi...Chiaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi. Mother here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're listening to this message,\Nit means you've returned home safely, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can go to Europe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozo-san, Nodame-chan, dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!\NWow! Crabs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so many???
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're from a VERY handsome boy....for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just kidding. It's Chiaki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Chiaki-kun brought them here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why Chiaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea....but he said they're omiyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, so you went to Hokkaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are gifts for his girlfriend, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, girlfriend???
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's a guy that can do the unexpected
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder what will become of him in the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next public performance of Rising Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the time being we're still preparing it
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoroshiku onegaishimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Culture page of Oshiuri Newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The column of the music critic whom\NI respect: Okawa Soutaro Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He contacted our Editorial Section eagerly
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,asking when Rising Star will do the repeat-performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, I had not made a wrong judgement!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma-san?\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakuma-san, I understand how you feel,\Nbut please hurry-up with your own draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh the stars that keep shining in\Nthe stark stark darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.06,0:16:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,personally sending forth your light,\Nthat even the Dawn has come out to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aaa, in the light of the ever-glaring sun,\Nyou're sending even more shining light!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirano-san, there's a call for you on phone #2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from someone called Elise-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh??
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make your own music!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play it according to the score!\NPlay each note one by one accurately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this...\NHai
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a competition, you must NEVER do such things as\Nincreasing the sounds or composing your own music,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because it will mean that you do not understand\Nneither the piece nor the composer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially this piece for the first stage is
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,merely used for dropping off the participants after\Nobeserving how they play the basic technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do unnecessary things,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because we have no time left anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that there is dirty money in competitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty money?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like for example, the pupils of the Juries are favored to win,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or sending oseibo to the Juries....\N(=year-end gift)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and inside the oseibo box,\Nthere is some money hidden at the side....is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have kone, Eto Sensei?\N(=connection to bribe or ask favor)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.10,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't it be better to send oseibo to them quickly now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT ARE YOU THINKING OF??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In Maradonna Piano Competition,\Nthe performers are known only by numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their names and from what music academies\Nthey come from are completely unknown
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most of the Juries are foreigners!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could anyone possibly send them oseibo??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't use bribery, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is ALL BLACK, isn't it??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nobody can cheat, then it's fine with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't worry anymore!\NI'll continue practising now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.27,0:17:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't worry anymore"??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she think that if no one cheats,\Nthen she can win the 1st place?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth does that self-cofidence come from??
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, until where have I practiced?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mostly, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't like Schubert at all, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why did you choose Schubert for the first stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?...Somehow...umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like wanting to try dating the type of\Nguy whom I have never dated before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that kind of feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ARE YOU STUPID??!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DATE A GUY WHOSE TYPE\NYOU HAVE DATED BEFORE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Schubert seems to be a difficult person,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even after I tried my best to talk to him,\Nwe can't be good friends yet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For my lunch today, I had crab omelette.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she has keitai?\N(=cellular phone)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it from Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.77,0:18:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:19:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a wonderful girl like her,\Nit's impossible that she doesn't have a boyfriend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuroki-kun, don't you think that\Nyou have misunderstood something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you two are dating, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since some time ago, definitely there's a big\Nmisunderstanding here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to wor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki-Sama!!\NChiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.58,0:19:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!! Oh no, it has come to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let us join this Oke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw your performance, and were very impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I graduated from Morimitsu Music Academy,\Nand for the time being I play...(trombone??)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you two there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fourth-year student at Momogaoka\NMusic Academy: Clarinet player Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.42,0:19:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Oboe player Hashimoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm number 2 in this Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that your jobs are already decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will certainly come to practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Chiaki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm like an indispensable thing so I don't have to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible that there'll be a vacant position for Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Rising Star orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be eternal in the future, because there is\NChiaki-Sama as the Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:20:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Then let's have an audition for everybody! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!\NHai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have not said anything about agreeing to\Nhave a repeat-performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.56,0:20:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now you can't say that anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided that on December 25th,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.67,0:20:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at Suntory Hall, our Rising Star Orchestra
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will perform Christmas Performance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suntory Hall??\N(=famous Hall in Tokyo)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we match, you know! *smooch*
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.00,0:20:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Kawano-san who arranged it for us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Classic Life doesn't mind to\Nbecome our sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, that is a great Hall in Japan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It accomodates 2000 people, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive, isn't it? We're aspiring to be the\Nnumber one in Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no, the number one in the world, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask you, Official Conductor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.98,0:20:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because Chiaki-kun is the most\Nimportant in Rising Star
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.96,0:20:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Chiaki-kun? Big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that stresemann is in Japan now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that he dropped by Japan while\Ndoing his world concert tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:21:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they said he was missing again from his hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought that perhaps he might be going\Nout to see you, Chiaki-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?? Chiaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Stresemann???
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real thing??
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WOW! Stresemann???
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master and pupil! A touching reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.93,0:21:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maestro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.26,0:21:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why didn't you send me\NNagaoka Mami's Photo Book?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,eventhough I have reminded you\Nby letter so many many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you came here now just in order to say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TO IU WAKE DE!!\N(=because of that, therefore, etc)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.78,0:22:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,today, after a long while,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lai, lai lai lai lai, lai lai lai lai,\NRising Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, what did you come here for, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.26,0:22:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Nodame-chan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame is now undergoing intensive training\Nfor competition
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.73,0:22:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nodame-chan in competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what has caused her\Nto have a change of nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.46,0:22:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki...could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.09,0:22:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you're able to go out of Japan now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's so,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.08,0:23:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then come to Europe right now.\N(he should say "go")
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will return to Europe next week
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.40,0:23:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki too, please come together with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next week?......So sudden..
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.96,0:23:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a Conducting Competition\Nin Vienna next year
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki must prepare for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki should quickly, even if just a minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,experience the music of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should feel the music of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I still have the Oke's repeat-performance to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.95,0:23:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't always oppose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whatever your Master tells you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.76,0:23:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever your Master says... is absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.52,0:24:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could change this Schubert piece..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.32,0:24:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a little break...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.24,0:24:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Schubert really a difficult person?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just talk about yourself.\NListen to the other party too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the score seriously upfront
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't face music seriously
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.33,0:24:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't enjoy music from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your condition now,\Nyou can't be together with Chiaki
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.32,0:24:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the score seriously upfront!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.83,0:24:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, from where should I start...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.90,0:24:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From here..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.89,0:25:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it a bit louder..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then quickly make it softer...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.78,0:25:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.02,0:25:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forte...piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.83,0:25:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,forte... piano!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.05,0:25:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accento! Crescendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.17,0:25:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accento..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.35,0:25:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?? There is one sound too many...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.47,0:25:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Change of key??
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.74,0:25:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?? Where was it....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the next, is it supposed to go up,\Nor go down?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.55,0:25:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is it now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.92,0:25:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth measure of the chord is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.66,0:25:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right....
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.43,0:25:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more please, from the start..
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful with the modulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.05,0:26:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.33,0:26:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One sound by one sound, there should\Nnot be any meaningless sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.09,0:26:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Can you see it?\NThe picture of this piece....
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.36,0:27:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maradonna Piano Competition\NHall for the First Stage
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.77,0:27:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to now, it's not sloppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.57,0:27:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she will keep it up till the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.42,0:28:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.53,0:28:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl....in just a sudden..
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.12,0:28:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O'Claire Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.64,0:28:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally there's someone performing wonderfully!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.77,0:29:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.15,0:29:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.77,0:29:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, Nodame passed the first stage of the competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.83,0:29:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then....I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case I want to convey it directly to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.83,0:29:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's the first stage, so there's nothing to celebrate...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.47,0:29:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't mind cooking for you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.20,0:29:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.53,0:29:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.68,0:29:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame has to return to Eto Sensei's house again\Nto practice the second stage
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.36,0:29:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry to make you feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.77,0:29:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.93,0:29:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.67,0:30:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the crabs were delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.15,0:30:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.19,0:30:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will Senpai go to Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.86,0:30:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.06,0:30:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will it be? Will it be around spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.39,0:30:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.21,0:30:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.37,0:30:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you don't want to go anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.39,0:30:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.34,0:30:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.11,0:30:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.71,0:30:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there is the Oke,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I will think about it some time later
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.83,0:30:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some time later??
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.24,0:30:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother, it is unrelated to you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.62,0:30:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.43,0:31:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,concentrate on your own matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.48,0:31:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's good that now you want to participate\Nin competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.29,0:31:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not unrelated to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.49,0:31:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.04,0:31:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to aim higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.28,0:31:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet you are talking frivolously now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.33,0:31:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have various things to do
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.42,0:31:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, the Oke's repeat-performance is already decided
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.35,0:31:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I suddenly go, everybody will be inconvenienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.76,0:31:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say lukewarm things blaming it on others!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.33,0:31:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai has talent, and there are a lot people admitting it..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.19,0:31:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.26,0:31:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone who's supposed to go out into the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.38,0:31:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't whine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.75,0:31:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a man with a small asshole!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.77,0:31:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, from now on, it is competing against time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.94,0:32:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the time of the final selection,\Nyou'll have to finish mastering this difficult piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well...don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.18,0:32:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to think about the\Nfinal selection now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.91,0:32:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, for the 2nd stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.31,0:32:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,practice Chopin's Etude and Debussy's L'isle joyeuse
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.13,0:32:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have learned Chopin's Etude in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.05,0:32:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the past??
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.82,0:32:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I remember it...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.55,0:32:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay you can play it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.25,0:32:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she can play this kind of piece already,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.99,0:32:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan is so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.16,0:33:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.26,0:33:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.62,0:33:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is not only talented,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.58,0:33:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she owns something that can move other\Npeople's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.52,0:33:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,something that can even make that Chiaki\Nbuy those crabs for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.72,0:33:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.82,0:34:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NWhen I am treating you for a nice dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.51,0:34:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember a bad memory of the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.31,0:34:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't remember such a thing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.93,0:34:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, Kozo-san!\NToday is the winning celebration for your two pupils.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.32,0:34:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, very good! You really did it well!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.72,0:34:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pays that you prepared it since last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.40,0:34:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. But Sensei, Noda-san is also wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.76,0:34:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Schubert! She already has fans now, I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.36,0:34:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to eat this?\N(can't catch the food's name)
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.80,0:34:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about technique, it was a close fight\Nwith that number 21 boy, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.32,0:34:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 21?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...Segawa Yuuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.85,0:34:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Segawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.83,0:34:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already won Oshiuri Competition while he was still\Nin High School,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and after that he seemed to be studying abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody must be thinking that he's\Nthe best candidate to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.38,0:34:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh....if he is that excellent,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.54,0:34:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then why didn't he participate in bigger\Ncompetitions in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Number 21, Segawa Yuuto??
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.95,0:35:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dec 25: R*S Suntory Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.60,0:35:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonorrow I'll be returning to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.49,0:35:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiaki too, come together with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.44,0:35:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't whine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.54,0:35:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a man with a small asshole!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.84,0:35:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crabs were delicious
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.15,0:35:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 2nd stage starts from 3 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.22,0:35:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.20,0:35:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have my own things to do
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.06,0:35:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cold boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.81,0:35:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.18,0:35:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without me, she can already do\Nwonderful things by herself, can't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.77,0:36:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, don't you know the reason why she\Nparticipates in this competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.26,0:36:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.24,0:36:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.00,0:36:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wanting to win ist place in the final selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.72,0:36:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.09,0:36:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She intends to study abroad together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.55,0:36:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to catch up with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.06,0:36:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with that determination, she managed\Nto come to this stage now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.74,0:36:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.94,0:36:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claude Debussy\NL'isle joyeusse
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.81,0:36:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, if you don't start to prepare now,\Nyou'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.58,0:37:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.00,0:37:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.65,0:37:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.67,0:37:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.25,0:38:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.20,0:38:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot go with you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.39,0:38:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will do....
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.30,0:38:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what I am supposed to do, then I will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.43,0:38:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Christmas performance of Rising Star is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.88,0:38:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will go to Europe..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.57,0:38:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You developed for the better, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.21,0:38:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay I understand. In return, for your last performance...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.17,0:38:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.99,0:38:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,half-heartedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.46,0:39:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His performance
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.42,0:39:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was good, wasn't it?\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.02,0:39:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, O'Claire Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.63,0:39:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, you should put make-ups properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.63,0:39:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arghh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.63,0:39:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, your face is upstaged by your dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.46,0:39:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing a pretty dress,\Nso you must be pretty too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.20,0:39:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And do something with your neguse hair!\N(=the state of hair after sleeping)
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.66,0:39:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ack! Always keeping such a face!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.14,0:39:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine more enjoyable things!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.40,0:39:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like feeling good being in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.39,0:39:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling good being in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.79,0:39:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Debussy himself...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.07,0:39:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,went for a vacation to an island in the South with his girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:40:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and composed this L'isle joyeusse in great happiness\N(=The Island of Happiness)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.32,0:40:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling good being in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.80,0:40:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mail arriving: Zero
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.23,0:40:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel good, feel good, feel good...feeling in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.68,0:40:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?!! Hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.50,0:40:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hai!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.93,0:40:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Chopin should be perfect, OK?\NImpress them with your technique right from the first piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.38,0:40:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you play just as you usually do,\Ncertainly you'll pass the 2nd stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.02,0:40:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.38,0:40:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, you're Megumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.94,0:40:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she can play this kind of piece already!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.09,0:40:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megumi-chan is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.75,0:40:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuto-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.48,0:41:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.52,0:41:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, hurry up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.01,0:41:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon the the 3rd part will start.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.99,0:41:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the guests in the Lobby, please return to\Nyour seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.06,0:41:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame-chan, will she be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.93,0:41:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.90,0:41:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O'Claire Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.88,0:42:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one will be that girl!!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.62,0:42:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Neguse Dress"??\N(=the girl with neguse hair in a dress)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.11,0:42:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon???\N(LOL, she didn't get it)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So first it will be Chopin...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.78,0:42:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Etude, they will judge the technique and the accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.88,0:42:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she can play it properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.71,0:42:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!! (stupid!)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.64,0:43:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.23,0:43:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such a messy play....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.49,0:43:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nodame?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.05,0:43:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she seem to hate playing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.33,0:43:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is such a thing like this possible to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.86,0:43:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you do it as I told you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.65,0:43:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hand is wrong!! This hand!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.41,0:43:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it as I told you!!\NYou!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.53,0:44:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OUCH!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.99,0:44:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over..\N(she won't pass)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.36,0:44:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,http://s-projects.org
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.86,0:44:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Final Version will be released